latestIgtvVideos.title: Maa ♥️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So this is one of the topics i have written on.. sharing it with all of you ! 🌸✨for all the mothers out there😇

Maa.. 
Meri khushiyon ka dariyaa..

Apni khushiyan har baar, har waqt kurbaan karke hame khush rakhne ki woh koshish..
Khud ke dukh bhul kar, hamare samne sabkuch perfect rakhne ki wo koshish..
Jaanti hu.. kaafi mushkilein rahi hongi, zindagi ke ye safar mein.. par maa mere liye wo badalon ka raasta banane ki wo koshish..
Kaise bhul sakti hu.. khud khaali pet rehkar.. hame thoda aur zyada khana khilane ki wo koshish..
Nadaaniyan, galtiyaan hamesha bhoolkar maaf karne ki wo koshish..
Mera rona, mera hasna, mera hurt hona.. sabkuch mehsoos karne ki wo koshish..
Aapka ehsaan kabhi nahi chuka paungi maa..
Kathinaiyon ke samne datkar khade hona.. ye bhi toh apne hi sikhaya na maa..
Maafi chahti hu har uss baar ke liye jab bhi apke keemti aansu ko andekha kiya ..
Jo bhi haara jeeta ..sab aapke liye kiya..
Aapka har kadam, har mod par mera haath, mera saath, kabhi na chodne wali wo koshish..
Mujhe hamesha muskuraata rakhne ki wo har ek koshish..

Shukriya maa..
Maa !!
Meri khushiyon ka dariyaa ♥️

-Fenil
